  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2901660/extras/2f5116807bc7a912611952add7c59047.avif?t=1730962075\" width=230 height=86 /></span><br><strong>Abyssal Blood</strong> is an Action Rogue-like/Survivors-like where you can dual-wield many types of different weapons at the same time. Lucy as the offspring of Lucifer CEO of Gehenna  Co., Ltd. She has to stop being a lazy teenager and do some bad-ass demons exterminating in hell.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2901660/extras/0d49774ec7a834fb27f120336b9bc785.poster.avif?t=1730962075\" width=196 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2901660/extras/0d49774ec7a834fb27f120336b9bc785.webm?t=1730962075\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2901660/extras/0d49774ec7a834fb27f120336b9bc785.mp4?t=1730962075\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Each Run Will Have 20 Minutes 2 Maps Each. </h2><br>Right now there are 4 types of weapons: melee, firearm, summon, and magic with all unique ways of playing <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>melee weapons can use charge-attack<br></li><li>firearm needs to be reloaded<br></li><li>summon can kill things for you<br></li><li>magic requires energy management </li></ul><br>You can dual-wield them for your own builds, EG: pistol with katana, necromacy with pyromancy, or 2-handed weapons like assualt-rifle and electric guitar.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2901660/extras/89c6cba2b7a636c67125f457e3e5b28b.poster.avif?t=1730962075\" width=378 height=378 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2901660/extras/89c6cba2b7a636c67125f457e3e5b28b.webm?t=1730962075\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2901660/extras/89c6cba2b7a636c67125f457e3e5b28b.mp4?t=1730962075\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2901660/extras/2f5116807bc7a912611952add7c59047.avif?t=1730962075\" width=230 height=86 /></span><br><strong>Abyssal Blood</strong> is an Action Rogue-like/Survivors-like where you can dual-wield many types of different weapons at the same time. Lucy as the offspring of Lucifer CEO of Gehenna  Co., Ltd. She has to stop being a lazy teenager and do some bad-ass demons exterminating in hell.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2901660/extras/0d49774ec7a834fb27f120336b9bc785.poster.avif?t=1730962075\" width=196 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2901660/extras/0d49774ec7a834fb27f120336b9bc785.webm?t=1730962075\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2901660/extras/0d49774ec7a834fb27f120336b9bc785.mp4?t=1730962075\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Each Run Will Have 20 Minutes 2 Maps Each. </h2><br>Right now there are 4 types of weapons: melee, firearm, summon, and magic with all unique ways of playing <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>melee weapons can use charge-attack<br></li><li>firearm needs to be reloaded<br></li><li>summon can kill things for you<br></li><li>magic requires energy management </li></ul><br>You can dual-wield them for your own builds, EG: pistol with katana, necromacy with pyromancy, or 2-handed weapons like assualt-rifle and electric guitar.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2901660/extras/89c6cba2b7a636c67125f457e3e5b28b.poster.avif?t=1730962075\" width=378 height=378 ><source src=\"https://shared.akam